"{\"uid\": \"wcjb.com-2024-07-04-parker-valby-secures-olympic-spot-womens-10000-meters\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"EUGENE, Ore. - Former Florida standout Parker Valby has punched her ticket to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 91, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prefontaine_Classic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1494261654603174e-16, \"text\": \"EUGENE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prefontaine_Classic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prefontaine_Classic\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"score\": 0.8906648310071725, \"rank\": 0.05625064697419769, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\"}, {\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Parker\", \"score\": 0.9908411340566438, \"rank\": 0.007955094055184686, \"text\": \"Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Candace_Parker\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valby\", \"score\": 0.9999999999656666, \"rank\": 3.43900611246172e-11, \"text\": \"Valby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Valby had a stellar performance in the women's 10,000M race, placing second in the event.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She secured her Olympic qualification by finishing in the top three.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Valby is no stranger to success.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is known for her prowess in distance running and hailed as one of the best in women's college track and field history.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Gator had previously attempted to qualify in the 5,000 meters earlier in the trials but narrowly missed out despite leading for most of the race.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her determination paid off in the 10,000 meters as she maintained a strong position within the lead pack throughout the race.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, she secured the runner-up spot, solidifying her place in the prestigious Summer Games.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reacting to her qualification, Valby expressed her excitement on social media, highlighting the significance of her achievement.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With her spot confirmed, Valby is poised to be a compelling contender in Paris, where she will undoubtedly be one to watch in the women's 10,000 meters event.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999963641405588, \"rank\": 3.6358727059381836e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by parker (@parkervalby)  Click hereto subscribe to our newsletter.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 WCJB.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}]}"